{"tid":1876790,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱落雨嗰陣屌到個基佬跪喺度喊","createTime":"2020-02-12T15:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T05:11:12.000Z","uid":150100,"like":38,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fd29fe8c105c76919d0a4ad016a7e339f38888","tid":1876790,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"咁話說本少爺係真男人嚟<br />\n識我嘅都知無論雨勢幾大<br />\n我出街都係唔會好似啲基佬咁擔住把遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁所以即使頭先落到狗屎咁<br />\n我都係戴住耳機，雙手插袋咁迎住風雨而行<br />\n正當我享受緊依種男人嘅瀟灑<br />\n突然間有把遮遮鳩住我<br />\n我拎轉頭一望<br />\n有個一睇就知係基嘅柒頭話咩遮埋我一齊行<br />\n我屌你老母，嗰嘢即刻火都嚟埋，一嘢將把遮拍落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基佬：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我話你遮乜撚柒鳩嘢？<br />\n未撚見過真男人呀？<br />\n屌你老母臭閪男人老狗擔乜春遮<br />\n雨水都驚你切咗碌柒佢做女人啦屌你老母<br />\n返屋企扮barbie玩hello kitty啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n然後個基佬開始喊咁樣<br />\n我就更加火撚滾<br />\n佢滴眼淚未滴出嚟<br />\n我就即刻喝鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知條撚樣真係即刻跪喺度喊住嗌daddy mummy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就話屌你老母你地啲基佬食屎大定飲尿大<br />\n全部都乸型嚟，冇撚柒鳩用<br />\n落個雨就要擔遮，俾人屌兩屌就喊到成隻豬<br />\n唔怪得之人人都話啲基佬有問題<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n我就覺得反正啲基佬都冇得救<br />\n屌嚟都嘥gas就雙手插袋走咗去<br />\n留低個柒頭喺度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主屌得好，啲死基佬唔屌唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係基佬，我落雨會擔遮"},{"pid":"b3972915d09b12eb5f072b13df4df62ce9f00b7f","tid":1876790,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccc59ef809cb78964354ac267aef2f01992cade","tid":1876790,"uid":224533,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Ws6ckP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Ws6ckP.jpg&h=d43b6509&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40bccb82816f71763870fba5b2cb8c95797cf760","tid":1876790,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"兩分鐘冇人回，連登已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e72f592952966ba9f4aa31f09e2fda09b7bec1","tid":1876790,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f12a6f5a027b04fab326ccc60e5c3163190f7e","tid":1876790,"uid":245282,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"Oliver吉魯 巴打幾時蒲返頭 <br />\n期待緊你屌九十後啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAnyway 樓豬 good ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dbe2e8523ff2469f3d4cd9f9ed728cfcb4f13e","tid":1876790,"uid":126133,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"樓主係1"},{"pid":"116eb4b005418aa558802dfc29783cb37800bb92","tid":1876790,"uid":193642,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"&quot;屌到個基佬跪喺度喊&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"